reviewText: Not wore the cost very slow on action  an I love  watching  buck Jones westerns
Faulty DVd. Stopped in the middle of the movie. Really cheap stuff.

Excellent crisp copy of this slightly unusual B western.  Nice to see these old Buck Jones westerns being brought out on DVD. Cost is a little high considering this is on DVD-R.  But if you are a collector of B westerns, this is a must have. Ward Bond is a co-star as one of the bad guys.
